{"tid":1607912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"閱兵--亡國之兆","createTime":"2019-10-01T05:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T06:37:42.000Z","uid":22360,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"67a34606c589a060459d0e050ac669c9d6e6d825","tid":1607912,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBVzW2P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBVzW2P.png&h=f7f55fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n讖曰：<br />\n黯黯陰霾 殺不用刀<br />\n萬人不死 一人難逃<br />\n<br />\n頌曰：<br />\n有一軍人身帶弓 只言我是白頭翁<br />\n東邊門裏伏金劍 勇士後門入帝宮"},{"pid":"51ec8e8b6c3b36e5e00ea15b17e7fae8cabda357","tid":1607912,"uid":312114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:40:37.000Z","msg":"巴打識野"},{"pid":"39df7e560b6aba3370dae90dfebe5e561023546c","tid":1607912,"uid":312114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"白頭翁 = 習"},{"pid":"8c0cf3f32f5d4883ce04accd2ee020fb6ba89a49","tid":1607912,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:41:30.000Z","msg":"大家夢遊前記得set Telegram 預設訊息<br />\n可以保護到手足性命<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCXiwqP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXiwqP.png&h=5c04cb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPush"},{"pid":"8dd693082fd432ab3edcab8f182dadd1202e468d","tid":1607912,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T05:41:50.000Z","msg":"今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成，冤有頭債有主，請大家對準政權目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a458d858843748feb460e1a